data.description: Welcome to your sunshine retreat in Saint James City on Pine Island! This 2-bed, 2-bath haven radiates cheer with a bright open living room, vaulted ceilings, and luxury vinyl plank floors. Bedrooms, strategically placed for privacy in a split floorplan, feature a master with a new marble-tiled shower and walk-in closet.    This worry-free home boasts new plumbing, wiring, drywall, and a brand-new air conditioner. The gourmet kitchen shines with new appliances, cabinets, and quartz countertops. A bonus room off the kitchen adds flexibility to your lifestyle.    Step into the radiant Florida room, soak up the sunshine, and relish the oversized lot with room for boat trailers, RVs, and a future pool. The neighborhood is a buzzing hub for walks, bike rides, and golf cart adventures. Discover local bars, restaurants, and a marina within a mile – it's a golf cart community that's too much fun to resist!    Don't miss this warm and inviting home—schedule a viewing today and step into a world of sunshine, warmth, endless possibilities, and the comfort of island living.
